    "body": "Hi @im-kapil The JsonRpcRequest you reference is really just the request body. \r\nI think this is more the level you'd need to log at: https://github.com/hyperledger/besu/blob/main/ethereum/api/src/main/java/org/hyperledger/besu/ethereum/api/handlers/JsonRpcObjectExecutor.java#L54-L55\r\n(we currently only log the body at TRACE level)\r\n\r\nFeel free to carry on the conversation in the #besu-contributors channel of the Hyperledger Discord: https://discord.gg/hyperledger",
